answer.en_GB: We get it - sometimes something just doesn't work for you and you want your money back. As long as an item is still in its original condition, we accept returns for free, subject to the rules below, including rules about fair use. None of these affect your statutory rights.  If you return an item requesting a refund within 28 days of delivery/ collection, we'll give you a full refund. Your refund will be issued using your original payment method.  We aim to refund you within 14 days of receiving the returned item.

markdown.en_GB:
###Q: How do I place an order? 

 A: To place an order, simply select the items you want to purchase, add them to your cart, and proceed to checkout.

###Q: What payment methods do you accept?

A: We accept various payment methods such as credit/debit cards, PayPal, Apple Pay, Google Pay, and more.

###Q: How do I know if my order has been confirmed?

A: You will receive an email confirmation once your order has been processed and confirmed.

###Q: What is your return policy?

A: Our return policy varies depending on the product and the reason for return. Please refer to our return policy page for more information.

###Q: How long will it take for my order to arrive?

A: Delivery times vary depending on the shipping method and your location. You will receive an estimated delivery date at checkout.

###Q: Can I track my order?

A: Yes, you can track your order by logging into your account or by using the tracking information provided in your confirmation email.

###Q: How do I cancel my order?

A: You can cancel your order by contacting our customer support team within 24 hours of placing your order.

###Q: Do you offer free shipping?

A: We may offer free shipping on certain products or for orders over a certain amount. Please refer to our shipping policy page for more information.

###Q: What should I do if my order arrives damaged or defective?

A: Please contact our customer support team within 48 hours of receiving your order to report any damages or defects.

###Q: What if I need to exchange my item for a different size or color?

A: We may offer exchanges on certain products. Please refer to our return policy page for more information.

###Q: Do you offer international shipping?

A: We may offer international shipping to certain countries. Please refer to our shipping policy page for more information.

###Q: What if the item I want is out of stock?

A: We may restock certain products periodically, or you can sign up for notifications when the item is back in stock.

###Q: Can I add items to an existing order?

A: Unfortunately, we are unable to add items to an existing order once it has been placed. You will need to place a new order for any additional items.

###Q: How can I contact customer support?

A: You can contact customer support by email, phone, or live chat. Our contact information can be found on our website.

###Q: What if I have a problem with my account or login?

A: Please contact our customer support team for assistance with any account or login issues you may be experiencing.

##Our Story: Crafting Beautiful Homes with Quality
markdown.de_DE: ##Unsere Geschichte: Schöne Häuser mit Qualität herstellen

markdown.en_GB: Beautifully designed interiors have the power to inspire, invigorate, and soothe us all at once. A well-designed interior can enhance our relationships, boost our creativity, and even improve our mental and physical health. A beautiful interior is not just a luxurious indulgence, but a transformative investment in our well-being, and it is well worth the effort.
markdown.de_DE: Wunderschön gestaltete Innenräume haben die Kraft, uns alle gleichzeitig zu inspirieren, zu beleben und zu beruhigen. Ein gut gestaltetes Interieur kann unsere Beziehungen verbessern, unsere Kreativität fördern und sogar unsere geistige und körperliche Gesundheit verbessern. Ein schönes Interieur ist nicht nur ein luxuriöser Genuss, sondern eine transformative Investition in unser Wohlbefinden, und es lohnt sich.

summary.en_GB: Our skilled craftsmen use only the finest materials and techniques to create beautiful, durable furniture that will stand the test of time.
We carefully curate our fabrics and designs for modern interiors, selecting only the highest quality materials and contemporary styles.
We take pride in our team of knowledgeable individuals who are committed to providing our customers with the best products possible.
